description	"Lab Specimen X-37

^2Weaponry:
- Sharp Claws
- Fire Breath
-- Based on Flamethrower
-- Limited Clip Size and Ammo

^8Attributes:
- Force Power Resistance (3)
- Wookiee Strength (2)
- Heal (2)

^3Abilities:
- Enhanced Jumping (3)
- Body Fluid Regeneration (2)
- -Shoulder Barge ^3[CS2]

A lab specimen, the first of its kind to engage Republic forces. Many howler specimens were tested on during the war, few have been bred to this age."